dex.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPslSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=fb0182fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"5706474fe208ec0aca307a077fc8bb53feaf5ad9","tid":1232485,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}